  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个消息备份的时序图。核心流程是：Backup Requester发起备份请求，经过XMTP Network找到Message Backup Provider，然后这个Provider把备份文件上传到Backup Storage Provider，最后Requester从Storage Provider下载并解密恢复。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Backup Requester",
        "XMTP Network",
        "Message Backup Provider",
        "Backup Storage Provider",
        "MessageHistoryBackupRequest"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，四个参与者。我确认一下：Backup Requester是向每个潜在的Message Backup Provider发送请求，而不是直接发给某一个对吧？这个广播逻辑是通过XMTP Network中转的？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Backup Requester",
        "XMTP Network",
        "Message Backup Provider"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Requester把MessageHistoryBackupRequest发给XMTP Network，Network负责投递。然后Message Backup Provider会轮询检查是否有给自己的请求，收到后开始处理备份。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Backup Requester",
        "XMTP Network",
        "Message Backup Provider",
        "MessageHistoryBackupRequest"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把前半部分画出来了：Requester→Network发送请求，Provider←Network接收请求。接下来Provider需要把备份文件上传到Storage Provider，这个我用实线箭头表示同步上传。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Message Backup Provider",
        "Backup Storage Provider",
        "upload"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "上传完成后，Provider要把结果通过XMTP Network回传给Requester。这里需要发送MessageHistoryBackupResponse，里面包含下载文件的URL。然后Requester再去Storage Provider请求这个文件。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Message Backup Provider",
        "XMTP Network",
        "Backup Requester",
        "Backup Storage Provider",
        "MessageHistoryBackupResponse",
        "URL"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "所以响应也是走Network中转，Requester同样要先Check再Receive。拿到URL后，Requester直接向Storage Provider发起文件请求，这个我画成实线。最后Storage Provider把文件返回，Requester本地解密并加载到数据库。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Backup Requester",
        "XMTP Network",
        "Backup Storage Provider",
        "decrypt",
        "database"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "最后一步有个细节：解密和加载到数据库是Requester自己内部完成的，不需要和其他参与者交互，所以应该用自循环箭头。另外确认一下，Storage Provider返回文件给Requester是用虚线还是实线？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Backup Requester",
        "decrypt",
        "database"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "用虚线，表示这是响应消息。自循环箭头也加上了。整个流程完整了：从广播请求、Provider处理上传、异步响应返回、到最后下载解密，四个参与者、十条消息交互全部就绪。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Backup Requester",
        "Backup Storage Provider",
        "XMTP Network",
        "Message Backup Provider"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
  ],
